Interface ISQLTableHandler<PrimaryKeyType>

  • Type Parameters:
    PrimaryKeyType - This is kinda self-explanatory
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ISQLTableHolder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSQLDataStorer, AbstractSQLTableHandler, AbstractUntypedSQLDataStorer

    public interface ISQLTableHandler<PrimaryKeyType>
    This is a handler class for ISQLTable. It directly interacts with the table that it is assigned to..
    Author:
    YeetManLord
